quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  68,1,"Noon walqalami wama yasturoon"
  68,2,"Ma anta biniAAmati rabbika bimajnoon"
  68,3,"Wa-inna laka laajran ghayra mamnoon"
  68,4,"Wa-innaka laAAala khuluqin AAatheem"
  68,5,"Fasatubsiru wayubsiroon"
  68,6,"Bi-ayyikumu almaftoon"
  68,7,"Inna rabbaka huwa aAAlamu biman dallaAAan sabeelihi wahuwa aAAlamu bilmuhtadeen"
  68,8,"Fala tutiAAi almukaththibeen"
  68,9,"Waddoo law tudhinu fayudhinoon"
  68,10,"Wala tutiAA kulla hallafinmaheen"